choices.text:
Write a passage about running that is short:

I love running. It's my favorite way to stay in shape. I can go anywhere and do it anytime.

Write a passage about running that is short:

I love to run. It's my favorite way to get exercise. I can run anywhere, anytime. It's a great way to clear my head and get some fresh air.

Write a passage about running that is short:

The best runners are the ones who enjoy the sport and don't see it as a chore. They love to run, and they run because they love it.

Write a passage about running that is short:

I love running. It's my favorite way to get exercise. I can go anywhere and do it anytime. I don't need any special equipment. And it's free!

Write a passage about running that is short:

I love running because it makes me feel alive. When I am running, I feel like I can conquer the world. It is a great way to release stress and clear my head. I always feel better after a run.

Write a passage about running that is short:

Write a passage about running that is short:

I love to run. It's my favorite way to exercise. I can do it anywhere, anytime. And it's a great way to relieve stress.
